headline: GTA Online
subtitle: In a Fix
content: Ready to run your own Auto Shop? Tune up customer cars for a nice reward but, really, this is the perfect front for some illicit deals. And by “illicit deals”, we mean breaking into prison, taking on the military, and infiltrating the IAA. You know, the usual day’s work. Auto Shops are now purchasable from Maze-Bank Foreclosures.
